OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,FThe most vulnerable families who rely
OL,7,Fon heating oil could benefit from
OL,8,Fextra support from the Government, as
OL,9,Fthe price of the fuel has soared due
OL,10,Fto the conflict in the Middle East.
OL,12,FOver forty thousand households across
OL,13,FCumbria alone use heating oil to heat
OL,14,Ftheir homes. It is especially
OL,15,Fprevalent among farming communities
OL,16,Fand rural villages, where homes aren't
OL,17,Fconnected to the gas grid.
OL,19,FGlobal pressures have seen the cost of
OL,20,Fkerosene - the fuel used in heating
OL,21,Foil - surge sharply in recent months.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,FCharlotte Graham runs a Bed and
OL,7,FBreakfast in Brampton near Carlisle.
OL,9,FShe uses heating oil and says she
OL,10,Fnormally pays around #1,500-2,500 for
OL,11,Fan eight month season. But that figure
OL,12,Fhas recently more than doubled. And
OL,13,Fthe increase in price is a big worry.
OL,15,F"So in January we were paying
OL,16,Fapproximately 62 pence per litre. We
OL,17,Fgot a quote just after the conflict
OL,18,Fstarted and it was #1.70 per litre.
OL,19,FIt's now come down to #1.30 per litre
OL,20,Fbut it's still very, very expensive."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,F"It's had a massive impact on the
OL,7,Fbusiness and on the prices of
OL,8,Feverything. And I can't just put my
OL,9,Fprices up because people have pre-
OL,10,Fbooked to come," explains Charlotte.
OL,12,F"Small businesses are being hammered -
OL,13,Fwhether it's small B&Bs, pubs in the
OL,14,Fcountry, community centres. A lot run
OL,15,Foff heating oil and they've got to
OL,16,Fstay warm.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,F"People want to come in and get a good
OL,7,Fwarm Cumbrian welcome - but at the
OL,8,Fmoment they'll be given a cold
OL,9,FCumbrian welcome and a jumper and an
OL,10,Fextra fleece to wear!"
OL,12,FUnlike gas and electricity, customers
OL,13,Fwho use heating oil are not protected
OL,14,Fby the energy price cap.
OL,16,FIt means they can be subjected to
OL,17,Fsudden price spikes and huge upfront
OL,18,Fbills when their tanks need to be
OL,19,Frefilled.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,FFollowing weeks of rising costs and
OL,7,Fcomplaints from those who use it, the
OL,8,Fgovernment has now confirmed over #50
OL,9,Fmillion of funding support for low-
OL,10,Fincome households who use heating oil.
OL,12,FOn Monday, Keir Starmer announced a
OL,13,F#53 million plan to ease the cost of
OL,14,Fliving pressures in the UK, targeted
OL,15,Fat customers who are "most exposed" to
OL,16,Fthe consequences of rising oil and gas
OL,17,Fprices.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,FHe also revealed the government will
OL,7,Fgive "legal direction" to make sure
OL,8,Fenergy companies pass on savings to
OL,9,Ftheir customers, "to keep bills as low
OL,10,Fas possible."
OL,12,F"I simply will not allow companies to
OL,13,Fmake huge profits from the hardship of
OL,14,Fworking people. This government was
OL,15,Felected to stop that. And we will,"
OL,16,Fadded the Prime Minister.
OL,18,FBut in his press conference, he
OL,19,Finsisted that the long-term answer to
OL,20,Fenergy security was "home-grown"
OL,21,Fenergy.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,F"Until we get ourselves off the roller
OL,7,Fcoaster of international oil and gas
OL,8,Fmarkets and onto clean, home-grown
OL,9,FBritish energy, tyrants like Putin and
OL,10,Fthe Ayatollahs will be free to attack
OL,11,Four energy security," he warned.
OL,13,FWhitehaven and Workington MP Josh
OL,14,FMacAlister said: "In many parts of
OL,15,FCumbria, heating oil isn't a luxury -
OL,16,Fit's the only option families have to
OL,17,Fheat their homes and keep the hot
OL,18,Fwater running. When prices spike,
OL,19,Fhouseholds here feel it immediately.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,F"This package will help ensure that
OL,7,Fvulnerable families in rural
OL,8,Fcommunities across our county can stay
OL,9,Fwarm and supported."
OL,11,FAs well as additional financial
OL,12,Fsupport, the government is also
OL,13,Fexploring stronger consumer
OL,14,Fprotections for heating oil customers
OL,15,Fand improved price transparency from
OL,16,Fsuppliers.
OL,18,FBut those like Charlotte, who rely on
OL,19,Fheating oil to live and work, say they
OL,20,Fare sick of just surviving.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773846666
OL,3,CHeating oil users 'hammered' by
OL,4,Cspiralling costs
OL,6,FShe adds: "The world is a very
OL,7,Fdifficult place at the minute.
OL,8,FEverybody is suffering whether you've
OL,9,Fgot money or you haven't got money.
OL,10,FThe country is reliant of handouts
OL,11,Ffrom the Government at the moment and
OL,12,Fthat is such a shame."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/9
